## 3. Accelerate FSDP2 Surface: What Is Implemented

This section maps each PyTorch FSDP2 feature to its Accelerate counterpart, and marks the implementation status.

| PyTorch FSDP2 Feature | Accelerate Abstraction | Status |
|---|---|---|
| `fully_shard` bottom-up wrapping | `accelerator.prepare(model)` with `fsdp_version=2` | Implemented |
| `reshard_after_forward` (bool) | `fsdp_reshard_after_forward: true/false` in YAML | Implemented |
| `MixedPrecisionPolicy` | `mixed_precision: bf16` in YAML or direct plugin field | Implemented |
| `CPUOffloadPolicy` | `fsdp_offload_params: true` in YAML | Implemented |
| DCP sharded checkpointing | `accelerator.save_state()` / `load_state()` | Implemented |
| `TRANSFORMER_BASED_WRAP` policy | `fsdp_auto_wrap_policy: TRANSFORMER_BASED_WRAP` | Implemented |
| `SIZE_BASED_WRAP` policy | `fsdp_auto_wrap_policy: SIZE_BASED_WRAP` | Implemented |
| CPU RAM-efficient loading | `fsdp_cpu_ram_efficient_loading: true` | Implemented |
| Activation checkpointing | `fsdp_activation_checkpointing: true` | Partial (see §15) |
| FP8 all-gather (TorchAO) | `enable_fsdp_float8_all_gather: true` | Implemented (experimental) |
| Explicit prefetching | Not exposed | **Missing** |
| 2D mesh (HSDP) | Via `ParallelismConfig` | Partial |
| `set_requires_gradient_sync` | Internal use in `accumulate()` | Implemented |
| `ignored_params` (per-param freeze) | Not exposed | **Missing** |
| Async checkpointing | Not exposed | **Missing** |
| `model.unshard()` / `model.reshard()` | Not exposed to user | **Missing** |
| `accelerate to-fsdp2` CLI | Implemented | Implemented (partial field coverage) |
| `output_dtype` in mp_policy | Not exposed | **Missing** |
| `cast_forward_inputs` | Not exposed | **Missing** |

